ral Park Ave., Suite 200, Davenport.\n\nThis is an all-ages event, with teens and kids welcome to bring a friend.\n\nRegistration for the event is required, and space is limited. For more details and to reserve a spot call 563-326-7504, emailprogram@gildasclub.org, or sign up onlinehere.\n\nCopyright 2024 KWQC. All rights reserved.", "title": "Free Summer Olympics opening ceremony watch party for families impacted by cancer", "top-image": "https://gray-kwqc-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/5S43YCKYGJAR5PQG7OT3SQMICY.png?auth=ded12ad72a11b0af9c9f24c0c12e7c059b34d72cf44354bfd289cb8c34681451&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "domain": "www.kwqc.com", "lang": "en", "author": "", "description": "Join Cancer Support Community Iowa & NW Illinois at Gilda’s Club for a free Summer Olympics opening ceremony watch party for any families impacted by cancer.", "keywords": "summer olympics,olympic watch party,olmypics,family events,family event,cancer support"}